            <article class="post-preview">
    <a href="https://darcynorman.net/2024/05/11/2024-week-19/">
        <h2 class="post-title">2024 Week 19</h2>
        
        
        
    </a>

    <p class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-meta">
  
  
  <i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>&nbsp;Posted on May 11, 2024
  
  
  
  
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;<i class="fas fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;5&nbsp;minutes
  
  
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;<i class="fas fa-book"></i>&nbsp;973&nbsp;words
  
  
  
  
</span>


    </p>
    <div class="post-entry">
        
        ⚙️ Work Students set up a protest on campus, expressing concerns about genocide and apartheid in Palestine. I walked around the protest area Thursday afternoon, and everyone seemed to be respectful, orderly, and engaged in activism.1
DISRUPT SOMETHING. NOT LIKE THAT! YOU&rsquo;RE DISRUPTING IN AN UNAUTHORIZED MANNER!
A few hours after I took that photo, the protestors were forcibly removed by police. They came back the next day, without tents. I note that our Premier said: &ldquo;I&rsquo;m glad the University of Calgary made the decision that they did.
        <a class="btn read-more-link btn-secondary" href="https://darcynorman.net/2024/05/11/2024-week-19/" class="post-read-more">Read More</a>
        
