            <article class="post-preview">
    <a href="https://darcynorman.net/2024/05/04/2024-week-18/">
        <h2 class="post-title">2024 Week 18</h2>
        
        
        
    </a>

    <p class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-meta">
  
  
  <i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>&nbsp;Posted on May 4, 2024
  
  
  
  
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;<i class="fas fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;7&nbsp;minutes
  
  
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;<i class="fas fa-book"></i>&nbsp;1319&nbsp;words
  
  
  
  
</span>


    </p>
    <div class="post-entry">
        
        I finally, after almost a month off the bike, got back on the fancy indoor bike for an easy-ish ride. I&rsquo;m hoping my excuses to not ride get less valid, and I&rsquo;ll be able to get outside on my real bike soon. My cardio is about the worst it&rsquo;s ever been. I&rsquo;m in horrible physical shape, and it&rsquo;s affecting my general wellness.
⚙️ Work Our D2L reps came to campus for a visit with our team, to help plan ways to improve the experience for instructors and students.
        <a class="btn read-more-link btn-secondary" href="https://darcynorman.net/2024/05/04/2024-week-18/" class="post-read-more">Read More</a>
        
